1. Importación de los datos

params <- list(
  Rec0="Rec0",
  Rec1= "Rec1",
  directorio= "/Users/estefaniagomezguil/Desktop/RecaidaRecod"
)
Rec0<- file.path(params$directorio, "0")
Rec1<- file.path(params$directorio, "1")
files_rec0<- list.files(path= Rec0, pattern = ".txt", full.names=TRUE)
files_rec1<- list.files(path= Rec1, pattern = ".txt", full.names=TRUE)
Grupo<- c(rep(params$Rec0, length(files_rec0)), rep(params$Rec1, length(files_rec1)))
files<-c(files_rec0, files_rec1)
print(files)
